	module or the checks cause a random assertion to be raised.

	* configure.ac: Use AS_LIBTOOL_TAGS to avoid notices about
	fortran.

	* common/Makefile.am (EXTRA_DIST): 
	* common/as-libtool-tags.m4: Slurp from GStreamer.

